---
// A deliberately stylized, designed mock of the app — an honest "look at the app",
// not a screenshot claiming to be the real build.
---

<section id="product">
  <div class="container product__grid">
    <div class="product__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">A look at the app</p>
      <h2 class="h2">The room, in your pocket.</h2>
      <p class="lede">
        One screen, one job: keep you in the interview. The question, your answer, and the
        live read on how it's landing — nothing else competing for attention.
      </p>
      <ul class="product__notes">
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">›</span> Talk or type — the interviewer reacts either way</li>
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">›</span> The score moves while you speak, not after</li>
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">›</span> Hint budget is visible, so you ration it like the real thing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="device" role="img" aria-label="Stylized preview of the Mentara interview screen">
      <div class="device__notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="device__screen">
        <div class="app__top">
          <span class="mono">system-design · L5</span>
          <span class="app__timer">14:22</span>
        </div>

        <div class="app__q">
          <span class="who">interviewer</span>
          <p>Your write path is hot on one key. How do you keep one node from melting?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="app__ans">
          <span class="who">you</span>
          <p>Salt the partition key, fan reads across replicas, and add a write-behind…</p>
          <span class="app__caret" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="app__bar">
          <div class="app__score">
            <span class="app__num">8.7</span>
            <span class="mono">live score</span>
          </div>
          <div class="app__hints" title="Hints remaining">
            <i></i><i></i><i class="spent"></i>
            <span class="mono">hints</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.85fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .product__copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.3rem;
  }
  .product__notes {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
  }
  .product__notes span {
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .device {
    position: relative;
    justify-self: center;
    width: min(20rem, 78vw);
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 18.5;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    border-radius: 2.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--ink-3), var(--ink-1));
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgba(236, 231, 221, 0.05) inset,
      0 50px 90px -50px #000;
  }
  .device__notch {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.8rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 33%;
    height: 1.1rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .device__screen {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    background: radial-gradient(120% 80% at 80% 0%, rgba(255, 106, 43, 0.12), transparent 55%),
      var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 2.2rem 1.1rem 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .app__top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--bone-faint);
  }
  .app__timer {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .who {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bone-faint);
  }
  .app__q,
  .app__ans {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }
  .app__q p,
  .app__ans p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .app__q p {
    background: var(--ink-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .app__ans p {
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--amber) 14%, var(--ink-2));
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--amber) 30%, transparent);
  }
  .app__caret {
    width: 0.5rem;
    height: 1rem;
    background: var(--amber);
    align-self: start;
    margin-left: 0.8rem;
    animation: blink 1.1s steps(1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    50% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
  .app__bar {
    margin-top: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 0.9rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .app__score {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .app__num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 680;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    color: var(--bone);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .app__hints {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }
  .app__hints i {
    width: 0.5rem;
    height: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--amber);
  }
  .app__hints i.spent {
    background: var(--ink-3);
  }
  .app__hints .mono {
    margin-left: 0.3rem;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .app__caret {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .product__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
